<td><a href="/wiki/File:Michelangelo%27s_David_-_Hilbert-Peano.png" class="image" title="Image:Michelangelo's David - Hilbert-Peano.png"><img alt="Image:Michelangelo's David - Hilbert-Peano.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/68/Michelangelo%27s_David_-_Hilbert-Peano.png" width="180" height="215" border="0" /></a></td>
